        "readme": {
          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<!-- AUTO-GENERATED-CONTENT:START (STARTER) -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org\">\n    <img alt=\"Gatsby\" src=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/monogram.svg\" width=\"60\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n<h1 align=\"center\">\n  @olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book\n</h1>\n<p>I love reading books. So the day it dawned on me that I could build a book with Gatsby was a GOOD day. By getting some brilliant friends to help me build this theme I hope to pass some of the goodness on to you.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#storytime\">My daughter</a> Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) gave me the Gatsby-book-building-idea, read the backstory by scrolling down to the end.</p>\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https://petra-rabbit.netlify.com\">Petra Rabbit</a>. It‚Äôs almost Beatrix Potter‚Äôs Peter Rabbit, newly narrated by Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) and I.</p>\n<p>‚Äî <cite>Ola Vea (41 #codenewbie and #booklover)<cite></p>\n<h2 id=\"create-a-do-it-yourself-picture-book-together-with-a-child-you-know\"><a href=\"#create-a-do-it-yourself-picture-book-together-with-a-child-you-know\" aria-label=\"create a do it yourself picture book together with a child you know permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Create a Do-It-Yourself picture book together with a child you know</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Automagically generate a picture book from image files</li>\n<li>Touch swipe to flip page</li>\n<li>Optional audio track</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ola will continue working on this theme while learning to code. New features will be added sporadically. You are welcome to make a pull request on <a href=\"https://github.com/olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book\">github</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/raae\">@raae</a> will help manage the repo. Ask Ola anything or give him ideas on twitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OlaHolstVea\">@OlaHolstVea</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://petra-rabbit.netlify.com\">DEMO Site</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"installation\"><a href=\"#installation\" aria-label=\"installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installation</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install @olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-our-theme-with-the-gatsby-starter-hello-world\"><a href=\"#install-our-theme-with-the-gatsby-starter-hello-world\" aria-label=\"install our theme with the gatsby starter hello world permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install Our Theme With the Gatsby-starter-hello-world</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>A book made with two random pictures, the Gatsby-starter-hello-world and our theme.</strong></p>\n<p>Use the Gatsby CLI to build a book, specifying the hello-world starter.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">gatsby new Your_Brutus_BADger_Book https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-hello-world</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Navigate into your new book‚Äôs directory</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">cd Your_Brutus_BADger_Book/</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>npm install @olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">npm install @olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Open the source code, delete the ‚Äúpages‚Äù folder and add two new folders</strong></p>\n<p>Open the <code class=\"language-text\">Your_Brutus_BADger_Book</code> directory in your code editor of choice and:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Delete the folder ‚Äúpages‚Äù at the root of your source code.</li>\n<li>Also delete the file ‚Äúindex.js‚Äù inside the folder ‚Äúpages‚Äù.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Add two new folders and two images</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a new folder ‚Äúbook‚Äù at the root of your source code.</li>\n<li>Create a new folder ‚Äúimages‚Äù inside your new folder ‚Äúbook‚Äù.</li>\n<li>Add two images to the ‚Äúimages‚Äù folder. You can use\n<a href=\"https://geir-g-1.netlify.com/02\">Brutus BADger‚Äôs Baby Rabbit Breakfast by Beatrix Potter</a> and <a href=\"https://geir-g-1.netlify.com/03\">Mr Tod with Baby Rabbits in his pocket by Beatrix Potter</a>. Both images are for the use of anyone anywhere at no cost and with almost no restrictions whatsoever. You may copy them, give them away or re-use them under <a href=\"https://www.gutenberg.org/files/14838/14838-h/14838-h.htm\">the terms of the Project Gutenberg License included with the Gutenberg version of this eBook</a> Click the link and scroll all the way down.</li>\n<li>Rename your two images to ‚Äú00‚Äù and ‚Äú01‚Äù</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Edit your gatsby-config.js</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">@olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        basePath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/my-book</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        imagePath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">book/images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        infoLink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-theme-picture-book on GitHub\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          url<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://github.com/olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book.git</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Start up your new Gatsby book</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"># Start up your new Gatsby book\ngatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n<p>Your book is now running at <code class=\"language-text\">http://localhost:8000</code>!</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-label=\"usage permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<h4 id=\"example-usage-with-audiobook\"><a href=\"#example-usage-with-audiobook\" aria-label=\"example usage with audiobook permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example Usage With Audiobook</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">@olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        basePath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/my-book</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        imagePath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">book/images</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        audioPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">book/audio</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        infoLink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Project on GitHub\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          url<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">https://github.com/olavea/gatsby-theme-picture-book.git</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"theme-options\"><a href=\"#theme-options\" aria-label=\"theme options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Theme options</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Key</th>\n<th>Default Value</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">basePath</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">/</code></td>\n<td>Root url for the theme</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">imagePath</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">book/images</code></td>\n<td>Path to folder of images to turn into picture book pages</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">audioPath</code></td>\n<td>null</td>\n<td>Path to folder with a single audio file (optional)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">infoLink</code></td>\n<td>null</td>\n<td>Adds an info button to first and last page (optional)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">infoLink.url</code></td>\n<td>null</td>\n<td>Url to navigate to (external or internal)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">infoLink.label</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">i</code></td>\n<td>Label inside button</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">infoLink.title</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">info</code></td>\n<td>Title for the a tag</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">imagePath</code> folder must contain at least <em>one</em> image file. The book‚Äôs pages will be sorted alphabetically by filename. We suggest using a naming schema similar to this ‚Äú01.jpg‚Äù, ‚Äú02.jpg‚Äù ‚Ä¶ ‚Äú99.jpg‚Äù.</p>\n<h4 id=\"additional-configuration\"><a href=\"#additional-configuration\" aria-label=\"additional configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Additional configuration</h4>\n<p>In addition to the theme options, there are a handful of items you can customize via the <code class=\"language-text\">siteMetadata</code> object in your site‚Äôs <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  siteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// First page will have siteTile as page title,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// the other pages follow this configuration &lt;page#> | &lt;siteTitle>.</span>\n    siteTitle<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Petra Rabbit</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Used for SEO</span>\n    siteDescription<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Almost Beatrix Potter's Peter Rabbit, narrated by Ola (41) and Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ)</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Will be set on the &lt;html /> tag</span>\n    siteLanguage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">en</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Twitter Handle</span>\n    author<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">@OlaHolstVea</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"shadowing\"><a href=\"#shadowing\" aria-label=\"shadowing permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Shadowing</h3>\n<p>To change the look and feel of the theme shadow components found in <code class=\"language-text\">components/ui</code>. These have solely presentational logic, while the root components in <code class=\"language-text\">components</code> contain the more functional logic.</p>\n<p>This theme has a persistent layout component <code class=\"language-text\">components/persistenLayout.js</code>. You will therefore not find a reference to a layout in any component. The <code class=\"language-text\">PersistentLayout</code> is wrapped around the whole site by <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/packages/gatsby-plugin-layout/\">gatsby-plugin-layout</a>.</p>\n<p>Why do we do this? Its so the state of the audio element will persist through all pages of the book.</p>\n<h2 id=\"storytime\"><a href=\"#storytime\" aria-label=\"storytime permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#storytime\">Storytime</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"a-good-day-in-the-morning\"><a href=\"#a-good-day-in-the-morning\" aria-label=\"a good day in the morning permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A Good Day In The Morning</h3>\n<p>One sunny morning Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) and I were reading Beatrix Potter‚Äôs Ginger &#x26; Pickles together.\nLillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) is my daughter. Ginger is an orange and yellow striped cat who runs a shop with Pickles the terrier. Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) was drinking warmed oat milk, I was reading out loud and sipping coffee.</p>\n<p>Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) said:\n¬´I want to make my own book.¬ª\n¬´Yessss!!¬ª I said with glee. ¬´Let‚Äôs build Ginger &#x26; Pickles, but with added PIRATES! Arrrh!¬ª\n¬´Do it NOW!¬ª golden-haired Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) said.</p>\n<h3 id=\"a-good-day-at-work\"><a href=\"#a-good-day-at-work\" aria-label=\"a good day at work permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A Good Day At Work</h3>\n<p>After a reckless ride on her green bicycle, I leave Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) at kindergarten and start my workday by typing ¬´Beatrix Potter¬ª into google.</p>\n<p>All of Beatrix Potter‚Äôs precious picture books for children where THERE. Like a treasure trove. Content free from ¬´this-content-needs-polishing-before-publishing-it¬ª thoughts to distract me.</p>\n<p>I started by firing up Scott Tolinski‚Äôs top-notch tutorial <a href=\"https://www.leveluptutorials.com/tutorials/pro-gatsby-2\">Pro Gatsby 2</a>.\nBefore I knew it, I had the Ginger &#x26; Pickles book deployed before I even remembered the poor pirates! Arrh!</p>\n<h3 id=\"a-good-summer\"><a href=\"#a-good-summer\" aria-label=\"a good summer permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A Good Summer</h3>\n<p>Do not worry! Pirates were added, kids from the kindergarten contributed and I kept working on a Gatbsy starter to simplify creating books even more.</p>\n<p>Take a look at <a href=\"https://olavea.carrd.co/\">the books I am co-working on Lillian (4.5 ü¶Ñ) and and her brave band of friends</a></p>\n<p>When the Gasby Theme Jam came around, it was the perfect project for my time at the summer office!</p>\n<p>And the rest as they say, is history (or a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/raae/status/1147430949598240769\">tweet thread by Lillian‚Äôs mom @raae</a>).</p>\n<!-- AUTO-GENERATED-CONTENT:END -->",
